 including remote sensing, chip-level\nEM analysis, and metasurface modeling, demonstrate speed-ups ranging from 3x to\n7x compared to state-of-the-art formulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Jun 2021 06:14:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 12 Dec 2021 00:38:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-14"}
