sues one should\nconsider when applying the lackadaisical quantum walk, besides expanding the\ntechnique to a broader range of search problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Jun 2021 09:43:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2023 22:19:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-11"}
